Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,成神陽太先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可以來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你說自己是研究所派來的實驗助手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這其實是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.21,0:00:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,請你立刻離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不通報警方已經是對你的寬容了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我還能再見到雛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我和那孩子預計要轉移去國外的機構
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,比這裡更先進的機構
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因此  你應該無法再和她見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:00:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託您
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.98,0:01:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,至少今天讓我和雛在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,成神先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就算只有半…半天也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.22,0:01:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,時間就只剩下今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能一起玩的時間  也到今天為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你打開心扉的  只有遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,雛沒有我的話  不會寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這是幾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:51.12,Comment,,0,0,0,,小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說這是最後的學習時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,至少回答我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我知道你沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那我無論如何都會把你帶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你一定要答應我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你願意離開這裡  和我一起生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,去年夏天  雛是和我一起度過的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,身邊環繞著家人和許多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想不起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還是記不起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,每一天明明是那麼的開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說這裡的生活更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,空…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對  是空  答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那這個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,和空相反  支撐著腳底的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,土?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好可惜  是更大一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,答對了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那這個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是意味著時間的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,時間  也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,時…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,時子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那…我找找…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是白天天上會有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是在燃燒的星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,別放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  我聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,雛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:03:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…再給我點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再多一點點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,別反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能就這樣回…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我要帶上雛一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,帶上雛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大家  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒能把雛奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你的歸屬就在那裡了對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大哥哥跟你說再見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,雛也要跟他說再見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再見了  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,…了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,少了?  什麼少了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,陽艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,陽艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,陽艾不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不能沒有陽艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小雛  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,陽…艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,西歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,陽艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候的情感  還殘留著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在也互相喜歡著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我都沒有察覺到這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,連這種感情我都沒有察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,陽艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,雛喜歡陽艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也喜歡雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡陽艾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我也喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,司波小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她選擇了能讓自己幸福的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,回到我們的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的公主殿下回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  陽太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  現在的雛已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼也不用說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的表情就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥  該出手時就出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,令我刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感謝這個溫暖的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,對於大家也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,剪頭髮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有點不甘心  但還挺可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她以前一直穿的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有那個就一點都不像雛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有那個電影就不能繼續拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,必須要穿那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼  天願小姐居然贊同了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思  我就這麼扭曲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,即便雛已經變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大家還是想延續那個夏天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,憑我的人脈  隨隨便便就能訂製一套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,錄影裡可以確認衣服具體是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒碰這個要來一發嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好哦  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要穿進那個環裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,從下往上扔就可以了  用全力扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  相遇的時候她也是先對這個感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,和雛相遇之後做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,全部是雛想要作為普通人體驗的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,打籃球  吃拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,作為家庭的一員一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,隨心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也會想要做一次電影的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那個夏天充滿了雛想要做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然想要遺忘那麼重要的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是個白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老哥你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那扔扔看吧  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,扔多少次都沒關係  直到扔進去為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了  好球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好  就著這個勢頭再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,先不要動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  尺碼合不合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好  最後戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  穿好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然頭髮稍微短了點  但是和那時候一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以重新開始拍攝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那首先是筆直地從神殿走過去的場景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,預備  開機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雛  你只要走到這裡來就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,雛  你是這個故事的女主角哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我演和你一起的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,之前拍過我們主演的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是拍電影的後續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,現在  朝這裡走過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只要抬頭挺胸的走過來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,加油  小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會一直等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的就好  過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣  到這邊來  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,卡  過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的名演員來演  肯定是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你做到了  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,彷彿電影一般呢  到現在我們經歷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,平凡的我邂逅了自稱為神的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,解決了各種的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一起度過了一個夏天  然後戀愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然也有困難  但都克服了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,像現在這樣  兩個人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們互相選擇了對方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以像現在這樣在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我決定了  我要重新考大學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想成為像雛的爺爺一樣優秀學者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,拚命學習雛所得的病的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的力量幫助你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,若是還沒有人研究出來的話  我來研究
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是人類的智惠無法涉及的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會去開闢道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這樣一來  雛就要和我一直在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,雛  喜歡  陽太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  自信湧現出來了  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼目標都沒有  只是碌碌活著的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,現在有了想要做的事  充滿了幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的感覺有生以來還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,為我指明了人生道路的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,或許真的是我的神明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,卡  殺青
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,努力到最後真了不起  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等製作好了來個上映會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這之後還有很多要做的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,選曲是伊座並同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,負責照明的你沒事了吧  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我待到最後嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天結束了  到了微感寒意的三月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  陽太要複讀了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,先冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你都考上八幡大學了  不去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,本來我一開始考也是動機不純
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且現在找到了想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好浪費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我替你去  我們換下名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我去整容也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  下面開始上映會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等很久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雛  我們的電影完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,雛是你想演女主角的電影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,雛出演到了最後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我們接下來要看了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  開始放了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,世界面臨著危機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,人們把這種無法解釋的災害稱為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,『世界的破綻』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒調查出來嗎  世界的破綻的起因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,現在魔術師們正在拚命調查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還請您再等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,王啊  這就是世界的大腦  SYSTEM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然而它的能源已經枯竭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一個個的迴路都開始停止運作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以導致各地發生了災害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,應當將國內的精靈使召集起來組成調查團
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這精靈的數量是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安  你這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼光著腳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,羅米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我馬上要去王都了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天長老和我這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只說了拯救世界的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這也太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然殘酷  但那是永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠是指直到死為止嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼  為什麼一定是安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,歌也唱的不好  也比較笨拙  沒有什麼才能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有拯救世界的能力是出類拔萃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早上就出發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,找機會把安帶出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然後兩個人遠走高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,世界的終結什麼的  與我們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,儀式要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是要犧牲安的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,把安作為活祭品  拯救世界的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,安就這樣  向著祭壇走去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有才能也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我喜歡安  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就讓這儀式結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快把他趕走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  儀式被…  迴路已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,維持世界的系統要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,世界要崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒啊  完全就是傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小雛是女星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  這樣可贏不了她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,導演的水準也很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這是大家美好的回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好的回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有那樣的東西的話  人就能很幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  真的是很美好的回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧  雛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那開始拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是花絮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小雛叫我把這個加在最後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  這次當了一回神有什麼感想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  一切都是那麼新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,每一天都亮閃閃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,回憶化為一顆顆寶石  填滿了好大一個寶石箱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就算世界終結了  一切都毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只有這回憶是不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是我永遠的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:22:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  你是這樣想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,今後要面對的未來無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,或許會非常無助  奇蹟也不會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是非常殘酷的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管如此我也會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拚盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,和雛一起活下去
Comment: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,（完結不撒花。）
